cardano/transaction/OutputReference.title: OutputReference
cardano/transaction/OutputReference.description:
An `OutputReference` is a unique reference to an output on-chain. The `output_index`
 corresponds to the position in the output list of the transaction (identified by its id)
 that produced that output

types/datum/ConfigDatum.title: ConfigDatum
types/datum/ConfigDatum.description: The main configuration datum for the entire protocol.

fields.title: fees_address
fields.description: The wallet address where platform fees are collected.

fields.title: fees_amount
fields.description: The amount of the platform fee.

fields.title: fees_asset_class
fields.description: The asset class (policy ID and asset name) of the fee token.

fields.title: spend_address
fields.description: The wallet address for spending-related operations.

fields.title: categories
fields.description: A list of supported project categories.

fields.title: multisig_validator_group
fields.description: The multi-signature group required to validate projects.

fields.title: multisig_refutxoupdate
fields.description: The multi-signature group required to update this configuration datum.

fields.title: cet_policyid
fields.description: The policy ID of the Carbon Emission Token (CET).

fields.title: cot_policyid
fields.description: The policy ID of the Carbon Offsetting Token (COT).

fields.title: dao_policyid
fields.description: The wallet address for the DAO.

types/redeemer/Action.title: Action
types/redeemer/Action.description: A redeemer for the `identification_nft` validator, specifying whether to mint or burn the NFT.

anyOf.title: Mint
anyOf.description: The action to mint the Identification NFT.

anyOf.title: Burn
anyOf.description: The action to burn the Identification NFT.

types/redeemer/GovernanceRedeemer.title: GovernanceRedeemer
types/redeemer/GovernanceRedeemer.description: A redeemer for the governance validator, specifying the action to be taken on a proposal.

anyOf.title: SubmitProposal
anyOf.description: The action to submit a new proposal.

anyOf.title: VoteProposal
anyOf.description: The action to vote on an existing proposal.

anyOf.title: ExecuteProposal
anyOf.description: The action to execute an approved proposal.

anyOf.title: RejectProposal
anyOf.description: The action to reject a proposal.

types/utils/AssetClass.title: AssetClass
types/utils/AssetClass.description: Represents a specific type of asset, uniquely identified by its policy ID and asset name.

fields.title: policy_id
fields.description: The policy ID of the asset.

fields.title: required
fields.description: The minimum number of signatures required for a transaction to be valid.

fields.title: signers
fields.description: A list of the verification key hashes of the authorized signers.

types/utils/Vote.title: Vote
types/utils/Vote.description: Represents the possible voting options for a governance proposal.

anyOf.title: Yes
anyOf.description: A vote in favor of the proposal.

anyOf.title: Abstain
anyOf.description: A vote to abstain from the decision.

anyOf.title: Pending
anyOf.description: A placeholder state for a vote that has not yet been cast.

types/wallet/Wallet.title: Wallet
types/wallet/Wallet.description: A wallet type for a non-smart contract address.
